articles.title: This country’s government vowed to eliminate TB by the end of 2025. It’s not going well. - CNN
articles.description: Relentless coughing echoes through the Mumbai suburb of Govandi, where families live cramped under tarpaulin and salvaged wood. The narrow lanes are waterlogged and airless, and here in India’s financial capital, a deadly disease is lurking at every door.
